column1: Different methodology was used by the Minnesota State Demographic Center
to produce statewide-level projections and county-level projections of
population by age. For that reason, the county-level and region-level
projections displayed here may not sum up to the state-level projections
for the same age group. However, total population for the counties and
regions will sum to state-level totals.
U.S. Census Bureau, Decennial Census and Population Estimates.
2020-2045: Minnesota State Demographic Center. Minnesota Population
Projections by age, sex and county, 2015-2045.
